<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7685234>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Metriocnemus erythranthei sp. nov., male (a–d). a. tentorium; b. thorax; c. wing; d. hypopygium." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7685234/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7685238>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Metriocnemus erythranthei sp. nov., female (a–d). a. antenna; b. wing; c. genitalia ventral view; d. genitalia, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7685238/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7685240>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Metriocnemus erythranthei sp. nov., pupa (a–c), larval (d–h). a. frontal apotome; b. abdominal tergites; c. abdominal sternites; d. habitus; e. antenna; f. labrum and premandible; g. mandible; h. mentum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7685240/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7685244>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Metriocnemus erythranthei sp. nov., larvae and leaf mines on Erythranthe spp. (a–d), larvae and mines on Veronica sp. (e–h). a. on E. glabrata; b. on E. guttata; c. on E. moschata (larva establishing new mine); d. on E. moschata; e. larva in newly established leaf mine; f. larva mining leaf; g. larvae in new leaf mines; h. larva in stem mine, with mining in the adjacent petiole." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7685244/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7685246>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Metriocnemus erythranthei sp. nov., pupation on Veronica sp. (a–e), adults (f–g). a. pupa in leaf mine; b. same; c. pupa in stem mine; d. pupal exuviae protruding from leaf mine; e. leaf mine opened to show vacated pupation site, with larval exuviae and gelatinous mass; f. female reared from Erythranthe glabrata; g. male reared from Veronica sp." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7685246/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

